              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The view in whose coordinate system the translation of the pan gesture should be computed. If you want to adjust a view's location to keep it under the user's finger, request the translation in that view's superview's coordinate system."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
