        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The x and y values report the total translation over time. They are not delta values from the last time that the translation was reported. Apply the translation value to the state of the view when the gesture is first recognizedâ€”do not concatenate the value each time the handler is called."
